<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 12:23:53 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中国共产党开除两名前国防部长因腐败</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-communist-party-expels-two-former-defence-ministers-corruption-2024-06-27/</link><description>据官方通讯社新华社报道，中国共产党周四以“严重违纪”为由开除前国防部长李尚福及其前任魏凤和，这是对腐败的委婉说法。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 11:46:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-communist-party-expels-two-former-defence-ministers-corruption-2024-06-27/</guid></item><item><title>台湾警告不要在处决威胁后前往中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-tells-its-citizens-avoid-unnecessary-travel-china-2024-06-27/</link><description>继北京上周威胁处决那些被视为“顽固”台独支持者之后，台湾政府周四提高了对中国大陆的旅行警告，告诉其公民除非绝对必要，否则不要前往。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 08:09:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-tells-its-citizens-avoid-unnecessary-travel-china-2024-06-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国希望与欧盟达成适合双方的电动汽车关税协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-hopes-reach-mutually-acceptable-solutions-with-eu-ev-tariffs-2024-06-27/</link><description>中国商务部周四表示，中国希望与欧盟就定于 7 月 4 日生效的中国电动汽车初步关税谈判达成“双方都能接受的解决方案”。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 07:32:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-hopes-reach-mutually-acceptable-solutions-with-eu-ev-tariffs-2024-06-27/</guid></item><item><title>尽管央行警告风险，但中国资金仍流入债券</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinese-money-flows-into-bonds-even-central-bank-warns-risks-2024-06-27/</link><description>中国国债期货周四跃升至新高，而长期收益率则触及历史低点，因为投资者无视央行一再发出的风险警告，继续将资金投入债券。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 07:22:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/chinese-money-flows-into-bonds-even-central-bank-warns-risks-2024-06-27/</guid></item><item><title>官方媒体称，中国共产党将于 7 月 15 日至 18 日举行重要的三中全会</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-communist-party-hold-key-third-plenum-july-15-18-state-media-say-2024-06-27/</link><description>据新华社周四报道，中国共产党将于 7 月 15 日至 18 日举行拖延已久的三中全会。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 05:45:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-communist-party-hold-key-third-plenum-july-15-18-state-media-say-2024-06-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国将对进口欧盟甲苯胺启动反倾销复审</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/china-start-review-anti-dumping-measures-imports-eus-toluidine-2024-06-27/</link><description>中国商务部周四表示，中国将对进口欧盟用于染料、药品和农药的甲苯胺启动反倾销期终复审。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 01:31:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/china-start-review-anti-dumping-measures-imports-eus-toluidine-2024-06-27/</guid></item><item><title>中国为应对致命洪水的城市提供超过3.16亿美元的紧急救援</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-provides-additional-natural-disaster-relief-funds-says-state-media-2024-06-27/</link><description>由于近两周的暴雨肆虐中国多个地区，造成致命的洪水和山体滑坡，中国提供了超过23亿元人民币（3.164亿美元）的资金，以帮助救援工作、应急物资和规划。</description><pubDate>Thu, 27 Jun 2024 00:53:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-provides-additional-natural-disaster-relief-funds-says-state-media-2024-06-27/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾大使没有在中国争端中寻求美国的补给支持</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/philippines-has-not-sought-us-resupply-support-china-dispute-ambassador-2024-06-26/</link><description>菲律宾驻华盛顿大使周三表示，在与中国在有争议的南中国海的对峙中，菲律宾尚未请求美国支持为其军队提供补给，并补充说美国只是提供援助菲律宾的“视觉”。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 20:47:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/philippines-has-not-sought-us-resupply-support-china-dispute-ambassador-2024-06-26/</guid></item><item><title>英国人权组织发起运动阻止 Shein 潜在的伦敦首次公开募股</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/uk-human-rights-group-launches-campaign-stop-sheins-potential-london-ipo-2024-06-26/</link><description>代表该组织的一家律师事务所周三表示，总部位于英国的人权组织“制止维吾尔族种族灭绝”已发起一项法律运动，以阻止 Shein 可能在伦敦上市，原因是对其劳工行为的担忧。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 13:39:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/uk-human-rights-group-launches-campaign-stop-sheins-potential-london-ipo-2024-06-26/</guid></item><item><title>中方驳斥美国特使有关阻碍人文交流的言论</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-rejects-us-envoys-comment-that-it-hinders-people-to-people-exchanges-2024-06-26/</link><description>中国外交部称美国大使尼古拉斯·伯恩斯周三的言论“牵强”，称其偏离了两国总统达成的重要谅解。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 08:17:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-rejects-us-envoys-comment-that-it-hinders-people-to-people-exchanges-2024-06-26/</guid></item><item><title>中国开发商世茂清算听证会延期至7月31日</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinese-developer-shimaos-liquidation-hearing-adjourned-july-31-2024-06-26/</link><description>中国房地产开发商世茂集团周三在一份文件中表示，该公司再次延长了债权人有关债务重组计划的最后期限，该公司的清算案已推迟至 7 月 31 日。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 04:54:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinese-developer-shimaos-liquidation-hearing-adjourned-july-31-2024-06-26/</guid></item><item><title>台湾报道中国“战斗巡逻”，北京誓言追捕独立“顽固分子”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-reports-renewed-chinese-military-activity-nearby-2024-06-26/</link><description>台湾国防部周三表示，中国已在台湾附近进行了另一次“联合战备巡逻”，北京表示将追查并惩罚“顽固”的台独支持者，无论他们身在何处。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 04:27:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-reports-renewed-chinese-military-activity-nearby-2024-06-26/</guid></item><item><title>秘鲁在总统与习近平会晤前缓和中国港口争端</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/peru-eases-chinese-port-dispute-ahead-presidents-meeting-with-xi-2024-06-26/</link><description>消息人士周二称，秘鲁要求法官撤回剥夺一家中国国有企业在秘鲁太平洋沿岸建设的“大型港口”的独家经营权的请求，这在本周两国领导人会晤之前缓解了紧张局势。</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 01:08:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/peru-eases-chinese-port-dispute-ahead-presidents-meeting-with-xi-2024-06-26/</guid></item><item><title>美国司法部称中石油将因美国出口违规行为支付 1450 万美元罚款</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/petrochina-pay-145-million-fine-us-export-violations-doj-says-2024-06-25/</link><description>美国司法部周二表示，中石油旗下的中石油国际美国公司已同意因违反美国出口法而支付总计 1,450 万美元的罚款和没收。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 22:22:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/petrochina-pay-145-million-fine-us-export-violations-doj-says-2024-06-25/</guid></item><item><title>外交部长表示，中国希望欧盟奉行“理性、务实”的对华政策</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-hopes-eu-will-pursue-rational-pragmatic-policy-towards-country-foreign-2024-06-25/</link><description>外交部长王毅周二在与匈牙利外长西雅尔托通电话时表示，中方希望欧方奉行“理性务实”的对华政策。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 15:41:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-hopes-eu-will-pursue-rational-pragmatic-policy-towards-country-foreign-2024-06-25/</guid></item></channel></rss>